  "body": "- [ x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\nEvery time I start my docker container I get this message\r\n\r\n```\r\n✔ Fetching solc version list from solc-bin. Attempt #1\r\n✔ Downloading compiler. Attempt #1.\r\n```\r\nWhat is the exact path \"solc\" is downloaded to so that I can add it as a bind mount to my container, so that I only have to download it once.\r\n\r\nI'm using\r\n\r\n```\r\nTruffle v5.1.47 (core: 5.1.47)\r\nNode v10.22.0\r\n```\r\n\r\nI've already read the docs and did not find my answer. I do not want to know how to change the download location, I want to know the default download location.",
